      "settings": {
        "heading": "About Mobolaji",
        "description": "<p>MOBOLAJI is a curated world of art, jewellery and clothing.<br/><br/>Founded by , MOBOLAJI brings together selected works, consignments and original in-house design across three connected worlds: visual art, adornment and dress.<br/><br/>The brand is built on refinement, cultural depth and considered taste. Each piece is chosen for its presence, feeling and ability to live beyond trend — whether that is an artwork for a room, jewellery with character, or clothing designed with intention.<br/><br/>MOBOLAJI is not simply a store. It is a house of selection.<br/><br/>A place for objects with beauty, story and permanence.</p>",
